context:
KR:
&lt;고마워… 얘들아… 대체 어떻게 온 거야?&gt;
EN:
&lt;Thanks, everyone... How did you find me?&gt;

KR:
&lt;미안해… 그, 그런데 우리가 여기 있다는 건 어떻게 안 거야?&gt;
EN:
&lt;I'm sorry... S-so how did you guys find us?&gt;

KR:
&lt;음…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Um...&gt;

KR:
&lt;할 말이 없네… 정말 미안해.&gt;
EN:
&lt;I'm really sorry... I don't know what else to say.&gt;

KR:
&lt;아, 그게…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Oh, that's...&gt;

KR:
&lt;그래도 고래 때 하곤 좀 달랐어. 어쨌든 대화도 통하고… 그냥 작은 사람 같았는걸.&gt;
EN:
&lt;They weren't exactly like the Whales, though. We could communicate with the gnomes. They were just like people... except smaller.&gt;

KR:
&lt;그거 좀 위험한…&gt;
EN:
&lt;Isn't that a bit dangerou—&gt;
